' (scil. ser|vitio). for euir. For þis gifte graunte & confirmacion & warantiȝinge, þe seide Roger & anneis his wife gafe to him xl. marke of siluir in wari|soun a-fore-hondis: & þat his gifte graunte confirmacion & warantiȝinge sholde be sure & stable for euir, he strengthid with his seele & is with-oute date.
